        "name": "Seal Fate",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You utter a curse that a creature will meet a certain end\u2014a death by freezing, stabbing, or another means you devise. Choose one type of damage from the following list: acid, bludgeoning, cold, electricity, fire, piercing, slashing, sonic, or void. The effect is based on the target's Fortitude save.",
